.RE

min_trans_id
.RS 2
First transaction id.

.PP
Value type: \fItransaction_id/0\fR

.PP
Defaults to \fI1\fR.


.RE

max_trans_id
.RS 2
Last transaction id.

.PP
Value type: \fItransaction_id/0\fR | \fIinfinity\fR

.PP
Defaults to \fIinfinity\fR.


.RE

