This function is only intended for testing purposes. It's supposed to test the \fIactual_reply()\fR return value of the callback functions handle_trans_request and handle_trans_long_request functions (with the additions of the \fIEncodingMod\fR and \fIEncodingConfig\fR arguments). It composes a complete megaco message end attempts to encode it. The return value, will be a tuple of the composed megaco message and the encode result.


