\fB                              Reason :: term().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Convert a token tag to a string

.PP
If no encoder module is given, the default is used (which is pretty).

.PP
If no or an unknown version is given, the \fIbest\fR version is used (which is v3).

.PP
If no match is found for \fITag\fR, \fIResult\fR will be the empty string (\fI[]\fR).


